SBS - Simple Booking System
===========================
Rewrite of previous project 'ICanHasSeatz'. (Which I never finished due to git-error)

Planned Features
----------------
- Easy configurable amount of seats.
- Custom tickets.
- Login-system.
- EMP (Event Manager Panel).
- Multiple language-support.
- Multiple themes-support.
- Suggestions?
